    <entry>
      <title>从负基础开始的小程序之路——重构</title>
      <link href="/2019/05/12/%E4%BB%8E%E8%B4%9F%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%8F%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E4%B9%8B%E8%B7%AF%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E9%87%8D%E6%9E%84/"/>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>只要对程序和用户有利，即使牺牲自己的时间也心甘情愿，绝不会因为自己可能受到损害而避开。<br><a id="more"></a></p><h3 id="前情摘要"><a href="#前情摘要" class="headerlink" title="前情摘要"></a>前情摘要</h3><p>摸了一个五一，再看看时间安排，期末又要到了，是时候和其他科目一起，捡起来小程序的复（预）习了。在脱离注释重新领悟当时的思路时，发现存在不少问题。正巧看到了<a href="https://namespacexp.github.io/joke/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">苏联笑话生成器</a>这个项目，击节之余觉得其生成逻辑有可取之处，故仿照该网站的逻辑趁代码量不大时重构程序，以便之后的进一步学习。</p><h3 id="重构记录"><a href="#重构记录" class="headerlink" title="重构记录"></a>重构记录</h3><ul><li><p>取消</p><ul><li>取消原本的直接预览想法，改为经过渲染后输出效果图并提供修正及导出选项</li><li>暂时停止对更改卡面边框功能开发的安排</li></ul></li><li><p>新增</p><ul><li>新增自定义输入项</li><li>新增对输入内容的有限度自定义排版*</li></ul></li></ul><p>*星号功能为待开发</p><h3 id="功能学习"><a href="#功能学习" class="headerlink" title="功能学习"></a>功能学习</h3><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">chooseImage: <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> (<span class="params"></span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">var</span> that = <span class="keyword">this</span>; <span class="comment">//此处经查找发现需如此定义，否则会报错</span></span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 选择图片</span></span><br><span class="line">    wx.chooseImage(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">      count: <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="comment">// 默认9</span></span><br><span class="line">      sizeType: [<span class="string">'original'</span>, <span class="string">'compressed'</span>], <span class="comment">// 可以指定是原图还是压缩图，默认二者都有</span></span><br><span class="line">      sourceType: [<span class="string">'album'</span>, <span class="string">'camera'</span>], <span class="comment">// 可以指定来源是相册还是相机，默认二者都有</span></span><br><span class="line">      success: <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> (<span class="params">res</span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 返回选定照片的本地文件路径列表，tempFilePath可以作为img标签的src属性显示图片</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">var</span> tempFilePaths = res.tempFilePaths</span><br><span class="line">        that.setData(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">          item: tempFilePaths[<span class="number">0</span>],</span><br><span class="line">          imgBoolean: <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#125;);</span><br><span class="line">      &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;)</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;,</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//字数限制，效果为仅能输入规定字符数以内数量的字符</span></span><br><span class="line">  bindWordLimit1: <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> (<span class="params">e</span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">var</span> value = e.detail.value, len = <span class="built_in">parseInt</span>(value.length);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (len &gt; <span class="keyword">this</span>.data.titleMaxLen) <span class="keyword">return</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">this</span>.setData(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">      currentNoteLen1: len, <span class="comment">//当前字数</span></span><br><span class="line">      limitNoteLen1: <span class="keyword">this</span>.data.titleMaxLen - len <span class="comment">//剩余字数</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;);</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;,</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="本周心得"><a href="#本周心得" class="headerlink" title="本周心得"></a>本周心得</h3><ol start="0"><li><del>摸鱼一时爽一直摸鱼一直爽</del></li><li><del>基础不规范开发两行泪</del></li><li>编故事易，编好故事难，编一个让人感兴趣的故事难度比技术开发还难。</li><li>好的架构与事先的计划能让开发事半功倍</li><li>看别人的demo可以提升自己的知识水平<del><em>所以说github真有趣啊我决定不自己写了</em></del></li></ol><h3 id="开发计划"><a href="#开发计划" class="headerlink" title="开发计划"></a>开发计划</h3><ul><li>学习canvas，直接生成卡面</li><li>美化应用界面</li></ul><h3 id="参考资料"><a href="#参考资料" class="headerlink" title="参考资料"></a>参考资料</h3><ul><li><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/YangBingX/article/details/80929404" target="_blank" rel="noopener">小程序单张图片 和 九宫格图片上传、预览、删除示例</a></li><li><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/c1e0574ee63d" target="_blank" rel="noopener">微信小程序之图片选择、预览与上传</a></li><li><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/q5706503/article/details/82827954" target="_blank" rel="noopener">前端—-CSS透明度属性opacity</a></li><li><a href="http://www.cnblogs.com/nowgood/p/Latexstart.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MarkDown 中使用 LaTeX 数学式</a></li><li><a href="https://namespacexp.github.io/joke/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">苏联笑话生成器</a></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
